---
ground_stop: >-
  <%= airport %> (<%= airport_iata %>) is currently experiencing a ground
  stop that's expected to end at <%= end_time %> UTC.
<% if affected_areas.nil? or affected_areas.empty? -%>
  Try using another airport nearby, as this is the only airport
  affected by this.
<% else -%>
  The following are affected:

  <%= affected_areas %>
<% end -%>
